title: Download is finished But stuck at 88% (MAC)
body:
Title says it all, I was recently updating for Patch 5.6 and it has finished after a long period, only to reveal it is finished on 88% with 0.0mb to download and 0kbps download speed!

Please help! been all day downloading (MACBOOK)

replies.body: Have you tried disconnecting and then reconnecting your internet? Sometimes refreshing the connection while connected works.
